high_descs: turn right and stop at the green table top
pick up the knife to the left of the tomato
turn left, then right and come around to face the front of the green table
slice the tomato directly in front of the lettuce
turn around, then turn right to face the stove top
place the knife on the pan on the left lower corner of the stove top
turn around, then turn left toward the green table
pick up a slice of tomato
turn around, then turn right and walk toward the stove top
place the slice in the pan next to the knife
pick up the pan on the stove top
go back to the green table
put the pan on the table to the right of the salt
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of tomato and prepare in a pan

high_descs: Move to the wall, turn right, move to the island, turn right.
Pick up the knife
Turn left, move past the island, turn right, move to the tomato on the island, turn right
Slice the tomato.
Turn around, move to the center of the aisle, turn right, move to the stove
Put the knife in the pan on the left.
Turn around, move to the island by the tomato, turn left, move to the island
Pick up a slice of tomato
Turn around, move to the center of the aisle, turn right, move to the stove
Put the tomato slice in the pan on the left.
Pick up the pan on the left.
Turn around, move to the island by the tomato, turn left.
Put the pan on the right side of the island.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife and slice of tomato in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the end of the green table and turn right and face it.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right and walk around the table to the first wine bottle and face the table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Set the knife in the pan on the left on the stove.
Turn around and go back to the sliced tomato on the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Set the slice of tomato in the pan with the knife.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk back to the table.
Set the tray on the right of the sliced tomato.
anns.task_desc: To slice the tomato and set a slice on the table in the tray.
